attributes.name: Hewn Log Storage Chest
attributes.description:
A chest that grants access to your storage, and increases your storage when placed in your home. 
It won't keep out any thieves, though.

attributes.name: Hope Storage Chest
attributes.description: A chest that grants access to your storage, and increases your storage when placed in your home. Made with the hope for a long, happy life.

attributes.name: Hunter Storage Chest
attributes.description:
A chest that grants access to your storage, and increases your storage when placed in your home. 
Holds your things just fine, and doubles as a canoe if you are in a pinch.

attributes.name: Iron Settler's Stove
attributes.description: This stove takes time to heat up, but will stay warm long after the fire burns down.

attributes.name: Iron Storage Chest
attributes.description:
A chest that grants access to your storage, and increases your storage when placed in your home. 
Built solid and sturdy.

attributes.name: Jade Painted Bamboo Blinds
attributes.description: Dragons are said to be able to create clouds with their breath. Drawing these blinds might increase the chance of rain.

attributes.name: Jade Weapon Rack
attributes.description: Are those the ancient spears of legend? They must be, to earn a place on this incredible weapon rack.

attributes.name: Maritime Posh Curtains
attributes.description: These curtains have the maximum number of tassels allowed by Aeternian law.

attributes.name: Maritime Posh Valance
attributes.description: The view out the window can only be enhanced by hanging this blue velvet fabric above it.

attributes.name: Maritime Ragged Curtains
attributes.description: These curtains are somehow both opulent and threadbare at the same time.

attributes.name: Mossy Rock Storage Chest
attributes.description:
A chest that grants access to your storage, and increases your storage when placed in your home. 
Cleverly disguised as a humble rock.

attributes.name: Oak Wine Cask
attributes.description: The flavor profile of wine aged in Aeternian oak barrels has been described by connoisseurs as "demented".

attributes.name: Old Wood Storage Chest
attributes.description:
A chest that grants access to your storage, and increases your storage when placed in your home. 
Perfectly serviceable.

attributes.name: Orichalcum Settler's Stove
attributes.description: In the Old World, orichalcum was so rare that it was almost mythical. Here on Aeternum, it makes for a very shiny stove.

attributes.name: Ornate Bronze Stove
attributes.description: This stove was a special order from a pirate captain who loved to cook.

attributes.name: Ornate Cast-Iron Stove
attributes.description: The iron will keep your vittles hot for a long, long time.

attributes.name: Ornate Copper Stove
attributes.description: If copper was good enough for the ancient Romans, it's good enough for you.

attributes.name: Ornate Gold Stove
attributes.description: This stove proves that you have money to burn.

attributes.name: Oval Cerulean Rug
attributes.description: The bright blue dye used in this rug was made with a mixture of azoth and oak tree bark. The color can't be exactly replicated anywhere else in the world.

attributes.name: Oval Gothic Rug
attributes.description: Bewitchingly soft on your bare toes.

attributes.name: Pirage Crew Keg
attributes.description: This keg is proof that you throw the best parties in town. The whole crew is invited!

attributes.name: Pirate Anchor
attributes.description: A fond remembrance of a ship blown to bits long ago.

attributes.name: Pirate Washtub
attributes.description: One benefit of being a landlubber: clothes cleaned in fresh water cause way less chafing.

attributes.name: Polished Marble Storage Chest
attributes.description:
A chest that grants access to your storage, and increases your storage when placed in your home. 
Scholars have not yet translated these Ancient runes.

attributes.name: Rectangle Cherry Rug
attributes.description: This cheery red rug is fully reversible. Unfortunately, the other side is also red.

attributes.name: Robust Wind Chimes
attributes.description: It takes a pretty stiff wind to rattle these chunky copper chimes. But when they chime, it is a sound to behold.

attributes.name: Rosewood Painted Bamboo Blinds
attributes.description: Slatted blinds are a marvelous invention, allowing you to spy on your neighbors without them being able to see you in return.

attributes.name: Rosewood Weapon Rack
attributes.description: This beautiful mahogany weapon rack comes with a scratch-resistant varnish.

attributes.name: Round Seafoam Rug
attributes.description: The beautiful color is worth the effort it takes to keep it clean.

attributes.name: Round Sunny Rug
attributes.description: A yellow rug shaped like the sun. Make you feel warm and happy just looking at it.

attributes.name: Ruby Brocade Drapes
attributes.description: The silver dragons embroidered into these drapes will protect your house from any strife that might try to enter through the window.

attributes.name: Ruby Brocade Valance
attributes.description: Aww, they're like tiny little drapes! That's adorable.

attributes.name: Ruby Geometric Rug
attributes.description: The sharp contrast of the dark red and the bright silver calls to you in ways you never knew.

attributes.name: Ruby Woven Floor Mat
attributes.description: The deepness of the red is so striking, no one will ever notice you swept all the dust under it.

attributes.name: Rustic Stone Stove
attributes.description: Keep that fire in its place, which is inside this stove.

attributes.name: Seafoam Posh Curtains
attributes.description: Keeps your cabin warm and cozy on cold nights.

attributes.name: Seafoam Posh Valance
attributes.description: Not enough velvet in your house? Here's an easy and fabulous fix.

attributes.name: Seafoam Ragged Curtains
attributes.description: No need to draw these curtains. They'll let the daylight through either way.

attributes.name: Starmetal Settler's Stove
attributes.description: This stove gives off heat even when there's no fuel inside. Unsettling, but saves on heating costs.

attributes.name: Steel Settler's Stove
attributes.description: This handsome stove is rust-resistant and waterproof up to a depth of 30 feet.
